description:
You are thrown into a mysterious speedrunning facility where the journey begins. 
Handcrafted levels designed to be puzzling and unexpected. Everything can and will destroy you if you move too slowly. On top of everything whole place is being tracked. Find whos behind all this.
name: Cyber Velocity Run
intro:
Cyber Velocity Run is a stylish neon, action-platformer featuring breakneck mechanics
Once you start you have only 30 seconds to escape.
